# hubot-webhook-cmds
Implement Hubot commands as via webhooks

## Installing
`npm install hubot-webhook-cmds`

## Example usage
```js
var hubot-webhook-cmds = require('hubot-webhook-cmds');

// Do whatever you want with 'hubot-webhook-cmds'!
```
